Frontend safety requirements:
- Billing page shows mock billing banner when provider=mock.
- Do not show payment provider secret values.
- Marketplace shows plugin safety notes.
- Plugin actions dry-run unless explicitly allowed.
- Enterprise export with secrets requires typed confirmation:
  CONFIRM_SECRET_EXPORT
- White-label custom fields escaped/sanitized.
- Onboarding encourages dry-run validation before production.
- Topbar branding uses tenant branding settings when available.
- Settings page shows billing/marketplace/enterprise config but no secrets.
- Dashboard shows quota warnings when relevant.

